posting_body: ['$0 DOWN, Move-In Ready NEWLY BUILT Home ~ Limited Availability!', 'Hurry, Appointment slots are filling fast', 'show contact info', 'ext.', '300', 'NEWLY BUILT beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath Sabine Floor Plan with No Down Payment Required!', 'We have a limited availability of move-in ready NEWLY BUILT homes all available at an affordable price.', "Every home located in the Patriot Estates community includes thousands of dollars' worth of custom upgrades, such as beautiful wooden cabinetry, all new stainless steel energy efficient kitchen appliances, spacious sparkling granite countertops and more.", 'Featured Home: The Sabine Floor Plan', '3 Bedrooms', '2 Bathrooms', '2 Car Garage', 'Flex Room', 'Community Amenities – Beautiful Nature Jogging Trails, Pool, Splash pad and more!', '$1719/mo.!*', 'to own this fabulous home!!', 'Call Now', 'show contact info', 'Phones calls are preferred - We are here until 8:00pm!', 'If responding to ad by email, please include your name, email address, and phone number.', '*P&I.', 'Price $320,900, 5.625% Fixed/6.716% APR, 3.5% Down, FHA 30 Year, OAC from third party lender.', 'Other fees such as taxes, insurance and HOA are not included in the sample monthly payment amount.', 'Prices and rates are subject to change without notice.']
